{% comment %}
  Product Detail Page - Conversion Badges (ATF Section)
  
  Shows availability status near product price (Above The Fold)
  
  NOTE: Trust messages and benefits have been removed to avoid duplication.
  Trust messaging is now handled by the CANONICAL trust_line block.
  Delivery dates are handled by pdp-delivery-estimate.liquid
  
  Usage in templates/product.json (after price block):
  {% render 'pdp-conversion-badges' %}
{% endcomment %}

{%- comment -%} Availability Status - the only unique element {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="pdp-atf-availability">
  {%- if product.selected_or_first_available_variant.available -%}
    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <circle cx="7" cy="7" r="7" fill="#10b981"/>
      <path d="M4 7l2 2 4-4" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    <span class="pdp-atf-availability__text pdp-atf-availability__text--available">Disponible</span>
  {%- else -%}
    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <circle cx="7" cy="7" r="7" fill="#ef4444"/>
    </svg>
    <span class="pdp-atf-availability__text pdp-atf-availability__text--unavailable">Agotado</span>
  {%- endif -%}
</div>

{%- comment -%}
  REMOVED: Trust Messages & Benefits (duplicate content)
  These items are now handled by:
  - trust_line block in main-product.liquid (max 4 items, configurable)
  - pdp-delivery-estimate.liquid (delivery dates)
  
  Previously contained:
  - "Contraentrega en todo Colombia" (now in trust_line)
  - "Garantía 1 mes" (now in trust_line as "Garantía 30 días")
  - "Envío nacional sin costo" (now in trust_line as "Envío gratis")
  - "Paga al recibir" (now in trust_line as "Contraentrega en Colombia")
  - "Soporte por WhatsApp 24/7" (available via pdp-whatsapp-cta.liquid)
{%- endcomment -%}
